{"tid":685334,"cid":14,"subCid":0,"title":"有冇巴絲做緊Business Development 工？","createTime":"2018-05-31T10:36:33.000Z","updateTime":"2018-06-19T05:04:50.000Z","uid":4453,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"9d7bfdb4789ed94baf778dfca05426d0a37c143e","tid":685334,"uid":4453,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-31T10:36:33.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7148bc9a3081cad3c03180200f601b237ffa22cd","tid":685334,"uid":4453,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-31T10:55:21.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b76dd6b8810e4fb7a14adbf2209648084c3d0dba","tid":685334,"uid":83920,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-31T10:56:15.000Z","msg":"sales"},{"pid":"0d6ce223ce730e86f232d3de5f22ba824cdec7d9","tid":685334,"uid":187962,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-31T10:58:50.000Z","msg":"BD = 不斷搵新客嘅Sales。<br />\nSales = 有機會係做Account Management, 亦同時有機會係搵新客。<br />\n<br />\n最好問翻間公司detail。"},{"pid":"969022d6715d734b386bbcde4f9cd5033b1167d7","tid":685334,"uid":7343,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-31T11:02:01.000Z","msg":"sales <br />\n自問毒撚就唔好做"},{"pid":"daf08f80c611a591fb36104c78d69a17bfb6f1e8","tid":685334,"uid":167164,"like":25,"dislike":0,"score":25,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-31T11:42:22.000Z","msg":"Sales=銷售<br />\nMarketing=營銷<br />\nBD=介乎sales同marketing之間<br />\n<br />\nBusiness development,顧名思義，係負責業務既發展，咁何謂業務發展？呢個可以係一個涵括好多function既position. 廣義d講，sales同marketing都可以係business development 既一部分。<br />\n<br />\n但點解會仲有個職位叫BD? 首先要講，一間企業既發展計劃有分長、中、短期，而所有公司既ultimate goal只有一個： growth. BD既責任就要以公司既立場鞏固或者增加營利模式。舉例，7仔以前淨係收八達通同現金，而加會收Applepay, wechatpay, 呢d就係BD既一種。當中要做既野有好多，要做business plan,要計ROI，姐係投資既錢要幾耐先回到本。假設公司拍板同applepay合作, implementation 要洗幾錢？裝左之後賺唔賺到錢？會唔會影響operations? etc... 而且仲要同合作方傾細節，同legal夾contract, 同marketing夾宣傳，分分鐘仲要做埋PM manage IT既timeline, 令成個project可以如期推出。<br />\n<br />\n成個過程就係一個業務發展既流程。<br />\n<br />\n以上係正統既BD需要做既野。不過呢，而家大部分公司為左想offer一個好聽d既title出街，基本上市面99.9%既&rdquo;business development&rdquo;工都係sale屎工<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 唔確定個role要做咩既，我建議你睇清楚人地個JD寫明要做d咩囉<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"73114672662eb1679c059f5ae1dbf82a08acb38e","tid":685334,"uid":4453,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-31T14:02:11.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ecb343c30372528f7c1ed3e39e94e973cbc67035","tid":685334,"uid":4453,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"0d6ce223ce730e86f232d3de5f22ba824cdec7d9","tid":685334,"uid":187962,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-31T10:58:50.000Z","msg":"BD = 不斷搵新客嘅Sales。<br />\nSales = 有機會係做Account Management, 亦同時有機會係搵新客。<br />\n<br />\n最好問翻間公司detail。"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-31T14:04:16.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"36e68a594357d8593ebf0df8dda02b8f56048211","tid":685334,"uid":187962,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"ecb343c30372528f7c1ed3e39e94e973cbc67035","tid":685334,"uid":4453,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"0d6ce223ce730e86f232d3de5f22ba824cdec7d9","tid":685334,"uid":187962,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-31T10:58:50.000Z","msg":"BD = 不斷搵新客嘅Sales。<br />\nSales = 有機會係做Account Management, 亦同時有機會係搵新客。<br />\n<br />\n最好問翻間公司detail。"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-31T14:04:16.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-31T14:11:33.000Z","msg":"唔定，要睇你咩公司。"},{"pid":"f556799b240d0b82000dd0a68628b3f7f18a909a","tid":685334,"uid":51250,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"cite